Package com.sjfc.fisherapp

Class Summary
DirectoryActivity Serves as a base class for DirectoryListActivity and DirectoryDetailsActivity classes; provides global variables and methods for querying the local database.
DirectoryDetailsActivity Displays details for one Faculty or Staff member as chosen in DirectoryListActivity.
DirectoryListActivity Displays full directory list with filter box; manages directory updates.
FisherappDatabase Implements local MySQL database schema variables.
FisherappDatabase.directoryPeople Implements local MySQL database schema variables.
FisherappDatabaseHelper Implements the local MySQL database for holding F/S directory entries.
